---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout currentPath="/about">
	<section class="section">
		<div class="section-header">
			<span class="section-label">About Me</span>
			<h1 class="page-title">Games are at the intersection of design and technology.</h1>
			<p class="lead">My background as a game developer focuses on interactive systems, full-stack development, and player experience design.  Using the skills I have developed through my professional and academic work, I aim to create engaging, interactive experiences.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="highlight-grid">
			<div class="highlight-panel">
				<h2>My journey</h2>
				<p class="card-text">My academic foundation started in architecture, where I gained an appreciation for design principles and spatial thinking.  
					When I transitioned into computer science, I combined my design and technology skills from both fields to 
					create immersive games, websites, and applications.  Today, I have worked on several game projects through my master's program and at
					companies like Mojang Studios and Booz Allen Hamilton.  Moving forward, my goal is to continue bridging the gap between design and technology to create 
					high-quality, fun games.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="highlight-panel">
				<h2>What I Bring</h2>
				<ul class="feature-list">
					<li class="feature-item"><strong>Design systems</strong><span>Gameplay prototypes, progression loops, balance tuning, and a creative spirit to every project.</span></li>
					<li class="feature-item"><strong>Technical expertise</strong><span>C#, Unity, Unreal, and Godot workflows, version control, on top of a plethora of other programming languages and tools.</span></li>
					<li class="feature-item"><strong>Production focus</strong><span>Clear communication, milestone delivery, and creative problem-solving.  I will do whatever I can to be a team player.</span></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="section-header">
			<span class="section-label">Skills & Mindset</span>
			<h2>Why I’m a strong candidate for your next project</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="grid-split">
			<div class="card">
				<h3 class="card-title">Creative Mindset</h3>
				<p class="card-text">Creating engaging interactive experiences unlike anything else is my passion.  My work is built to be fun, balanced, and versatile.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3 class="card-title">Production-Ready Delivery</h3>
				<p class="card-text">Prioritizing clean implementation, documentation, and handoff is integral to my work.  I ensure that team can move quickly without compromising quality.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3 class="card-title">Cross-Disciplinary Collaboration</h3>
				<p class="card-text">Clear communication with designers, artists, and engineers is essential to keep scope realistic and deliver on shared creative goals.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3 class="card-title">Passion for Growth</h3>
				<p class="card-text">Learning and improving continually to enchance my skills is something that I take pride in.  Having a growth mindset is crucial in today's rapidly evolving industry.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
